ed system, are accumulated first in the BGT whereafter they\nare stacked in the ultra-high vacuum HFT, where we have been able to trap\n1.4(2) x 10^9 positrons in 1100 seconds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 May 2022 19:52:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-14"}
