 image acquisition techniques will be used, such\nas: filtering, Gaussian adjustment, and use of regions of interferences. With\nall this, the data extracted from the telescope will be optimized to achieve\nthe desired results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 May 2022 15:47:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-13"}
